logwatcherd (2.0.20160420a) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * New release
  - FIX: Minor correction in README file
  - ADD: Data 'Conditioners'
  - ADD: Allow to include configuration files
  - MOD: Allow daemon to exit faster when interrupted
  - FIX: Wait for daemon to stop in init script (and be systemd friendly)
  - ADD: New 'respawn' configuration parameter allows watcher to respawn        
         in case of error

